---
---

<!-- PAS Framework: Problem → Agitate → Solve -->
<section class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- PROBLEM -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="inline-block text-academy-teal text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Sound Familiar?</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-brand-charcoal leading-tight mb-6">
        You Love Your Dog. But You Can't Leave Them <span class="text-academy-teal">Anywhere.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Pain points — their exact words -->
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-neutral-200">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.28 7.22a.75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06L8.94 10l-1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06L10 11.06l1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06L11.06 10l1.72-1.72a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06L10 8.94 8.28 7.22z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">"My dog got kicked out of their last daycare for being too rough"</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-neutral-200">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.28 7.22a.75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06L8.94 10l-1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06L10 11.06l1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06L11.06 10l1.72-1.72a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06L10 8.94 8.28 7.22z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">"I work all day and feel guilty leaving them home alone"</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-neutral-200">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.28 7.22a.75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06L8.94 10l-1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06L10 11.06l1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06L11.06 10l1.72-1.72a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06L10 8.94 8.28 7.22z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">"My dog is nervous around other dogs and I don't know how to help"</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-neutral-200">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.28 7.22a.75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06L8.94 10l-1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06L10 11.06l1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06L11.06 10l1.72-1.72a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06L10 8.94 8.28 7.22z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">"Every daycare I've been to is just chaos — 30 dogs with one person watching"</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-neutral-200">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.28 7.22a.75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06L8.94 10l-1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06L10 11.06l1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06L11.06 10l1.72-1.72a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06L10 8.94 8.28 7.22z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">"My dog comes home from daycare more hyper than when they left"</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-neutral-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-neutral-200">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.28 7.22a.75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06L8.94 10l-1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06 1.06L10 11.06l1.72 1.72a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06L11.06 10l1.72-1.72a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06L10 8.94 8.28 7.22z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">"I'm scared my dog will get hurt at a facility that doesn't know what they're doing"</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- AGITATE -->
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-neutral-200 mb-12">
      <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-brand-charcoal mb-4">Here's what most daycares won't tell you:</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Most daycares are glorified holding pens. They throw 20–40 dogs in a room, hire part-time staff with zero behaviour training, and hope nothing goes wrong. Your dog doesn't learn anything. They don't build confidence. They just get overstimulated — and come home worse than they left.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
        If your dog is nervous, reactive, or high-energy — those places are a recipe for disaster. And if they get kicked out? Now you're back to square one with an even more stressed dog.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- SOLVE -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black text-brand-charcoal mb-4">
        Academy Daycare is <span class="text-academy-teal">the opposite of that.</span>
      </h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Run by canine behaviour specialists with 15 years of experience making dogs social — and keeping them social for life. We can handle any dog. Play is structured, rules are respected, and your dog comes home calmer, more confident, and better behaved.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-academy-teal text-white text-base font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-academy-teal-dark transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg shadow-academy-teal/25 hover:shadow-academy-teal/40 hover:-translate-y-0.5">
        Book Your Dog's Assessment
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
